# Docker Container Lifecycle

```text
Docker Image
      │
      ▼
docker run
      │
      ▼
Container Created
      │
      ▼
Running
      │
      ├────────► docker stop
      │               │
      │               ▼
      │            Exited
      │               │
      │               ▼
      │          docker start
      │               │
      ▼               ▼
Running ◄──── docker restart

Running
      │
      ▼
docker exec
(Open Interactive Terminal)

Running
      │
      ▼
docker logs
(View Application Logs)

Running / Stopped
      │
      ▼
docker cp
(Copy files between Host and Container)
```

